pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: nav-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 1280, 40]
    shapeName: rect
    fill: {type: solid, color: "$primary"}

  - elementId: nav-ch1
    elementType: text
    bounds: [0, 0, 320, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>01 项目背景与目标</p>

  - elementId: nav-ch2
    elementType: text
    bounds: [320, 0, 320, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFF80"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>02 系统架构与核心功能</p>

  - elementId: nav-ch3
    elementType: text
    bounds: [640, 0, 320, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFF80"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>03 技术亮点与实现</p>

  - elementId: nav-ch4
    elementType: text
    bounds: [960, 0, 320, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFF80"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>04 项目成果与展望</p>

  - elementId: nav-indicator
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 40, 320, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border: {style: solid, width: 3, color: "$accent"}

  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 55, 500, 42]
    content:
      style: "$heading"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>项目背景与目标</p>

  - elementId: title-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 100, 50, 4]
    shapeName: rect
    fill: {type: solid, color: "$accent"}

  - elementId: pain-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [60, 130, 32, 32]
    iconName: "fas:circle-exclamation"
    fill: {type: solid, color: "$accent"}

  - elementId: pain-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [105, 130, 200, 32]
    content:
      style: "$subheading"
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$accent"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>痛点</p>

  - elementId: pain-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 175, 550, 165]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 18
      lineHeight: 1.8
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>• 课程论文写作耗时漫长，学生时间压力大</p>
        <p>• 缺乏学术写作经验，难以组织论文章节</p>
        <p>• 格式排版繁琐，引用规范易出错</p>
        <p>• 参考文献查找与整理效率低下</p>

  - elementId: opp-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [60, 345, 32, 32]
    iconName: "fas:lightbulb"
    fill: {type: solid, color: "$primary"}

  - elementId: opp-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [105, 345, 200, 32]
    content:
      style: "$subheading"
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>机遇</p>

  - elementId: opp-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 390, 550, 120]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 18
      lineHeight: 1.8
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>• DeepSeek 大模型具备强大的文本生成</p>
        <p>  和语言理解能力</p>
        <p>• AI 可辅助完成论文写作全流程</p>

  - elementId: goal-card-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [660, 130, 560, 340]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill: {type: solid, color: "$light"}

  - elementId: goal-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [690, 150, 200, 32]
    content:
      style: "$subheading"
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>项目目标</p>

  - elementId: goal-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [690, 195, 500, 255]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 18
      lineHeight: 1.8
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>构建一站式 AI 论文辅助写作平台，覆盖：</p>
        <p> </p>
        <p><strong>生成</strong> — 输入主题，AI 输出完整论文</p>
        <p><strong>润色</strong> — 四种模式，精准改写</p>
        <p><strong>排版</strong> — 多模板，一键规范</p>
        <p><strong>导出</strong> — 标准 Word，直接提交</p>

  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1180, 680, 60, 25]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>03</p>
